('Desert Gushers', 'desert-gushers', 'indica', 14.0, 0.6, array['hungry', 'uplifted', 'energetic']::text[], array['floral', 'skunk', 'mango']::text[], array['ocimene', 'linalool', 'pinene']::text[], 'easy', 9, '550-650 g/m²', '650-800 g/plant', 'Desert Gushers — An indica known for deep body relaxation, best reserved for evenings and lazy nights in. Expect floral, skunk, mango flavors with dominant ocimene, most often leaving users feeling hungry and uplifted.'),
('Desert Tangie', 'desert-tangie', 'hybrid', 23.5, 1.0, array['tingly', 'focused', 'creative', 'talkative', 'hungry']::text[], array['pepper', 'lemon', 'floral']::text[], array['limonene', 'pinene', 'humulene']::text[], 'hard', 8, '375-475 g/m²', '450-600 g/plant', 'Desert Tangie — A balanced hybrid offering the best of both worlds — a smooth head high that settles into gentle body calm. Expect pepper, lemon, floral flavors with dominant limonene, most often leaving users feeling tingly and focused.'),
('Desert Mimosa', 'desert-mimosa', 'indica', 20.9, 1.0, array['tingly', 'giggly', 'uplifted']::text[], array['earthy', 'mango', 'grape']::text[], array['humulene', 'limonene', 'caryophyllene']::text[], 'easy', 8, '525-625 g/m²', '500-650 g/plant', 'Desert Mimosa — An indica known for deep body relaxation, best reserved for evenings and lazy nights in. Expect earthy, mango, grape flavors with dominant humulene, most often leaving users feeling tingly and giggly.')
